        public boolean addNewTaskViewToDate(java.util.Calendar date,
                                    int taskId,
                                    java.lang.String description,
                                    java.lang.String time,
                                    boolean done)
        Adds a TaskView to a TaskViewDate.

        Task View is a View that displays all information of a single task in it. pre-cond: date cannot be null, description cannot be empty, taskId cannot be negative

        Parameters:
        date - date of new task to add
        taskId - taskid of new task to add
        description - description of new task to add
        time - time of new task to add
        done - status of new task to add
        Returns:
        boolean status of operation
